<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-11"><a href="#Technology.2C_science.2C_and_engineering"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Technology, science, and engineering</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-12"><a href="#Gunpowder_warfare"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Gunpowder warfare</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-13"><a href="#Measuring_distance_and_mechanical_navigation"><span class="tocnumber">4.2</span> <span class="toctext">Measuring distance and mechanical navigation</span></a></li>
