<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Song_Dynasty&action=edit&section=21.php.html" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span></h2>
<p><span id="cnote_a"><b><a href="#ref_a">^</a></b></span>&#160;<b>a:</b>&#160;During the reign of the Song Dynasty the world population grew from about 250 million to approximately 330 million, a difference of 80 million. Please also see <a href="Medieval_demography" title="Medieval demography">Medieval demography</a>.<br /></p>
