<li id="cite_note-ebrey_et_al_2006_236-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-ebrey_et_al_2006_236_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ebrey_et_al_2006_236_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFEbreyWalthallPalais2006">Ebrey, Walthall &amp; Palais 2006</a>, p.&#160;236.</span></li>
