<li><span class="citation" id="CITEREFVeeckPannellSmithHuang2007">Veeck, Gregory; Pannell, Clifton W.; Smith, Christopher J.; Huang, Youqin (2007), <i>China's Geography: Globalization and the Dynamics of Political, Economic, and Social Change</i>, Lanham: Rowman &amp; Littlefield Publishers, <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-7425-5402-3" title="Special:BookSources/0-7425-5402-3">0-7425-5402-3</a></span></li>
